text: Dom Nicolas I Kongo Nicolau I Misaki mia Nimi was ruler of the Kingdom of Kongo as a member of the Kimpanzu house from 1752 until sometime after 1758, during the rotating houses period established by Pedro IV.History Files: Kingdom of Kongo (http://www.historyfiles.co.uk/KingListsAfrica/AfricaAngola.htm) ==References== Category:Manikongo of Kongo
title: Nicolau I of Kongo
